OBS Continuous Integration
==========================

This directory contains scripts and configuration templates to setup a
Continuous Integration (CI) environment based on Hudson/Jenkins.


OBS job setup
-------------

The following list of CI jobs should be set up as described in their
corresponding helper scripts:

 * obs_common
 * obs_testsuite_api


Plugin dependencies
-------------------

Next to Hudson/Jenkins, you need to have the following list of plugins
installed:

 * Copy Artifact Plugin
 * GIT Plugin
 * Rake plugin
 * Ruby Plugin
 * Ruby metrics plugin

